Package edu.uw.cs.cse461.util

Interface Summary
ConfigManagerInterface The public interface for the ConfigManager class, which provides a minimal wrapper extending java.util.Properties (so public methods of that class may be used as well as the ones listed here).
 

Class Summary
Base64 Encodes and decodes to and from Base64 notation.
Base64.InputStream A Base64.InputStream will read data from another java.io.InputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
Base64.OutputStream A Base64.OutputStream will write data to another java.io.OutputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
ConfigManager A class intended to make parsing the config.ini file easier.
IPFinder Console implementation of a class that tries to determine "the IP address" of the machine we're running on.
Log

SampledStatistic.ElapsedTimeInterval  
SampledStatistic.TransferRate Class to simplify making transfer rate measurements.
SampledStatistic.TransferRateInterval  
 

Enum Summary
